Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你剪头发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀要剪到耳朵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村一定很适合穿水手服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,都说过我不会穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你脸这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,头发又这么清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊 你绝对剪太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的发根都在痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢 今天天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,牛头不对马嘴的对话好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学与宫村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,开始播放了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,jiang～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,井浦你的出场就到此为止了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还是看在人气投票里你是第一名的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,诶诶诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开始是新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和刚高一入学的时候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到了高三就没什么特别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,除了觉得春假太短暂以外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也没别的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是一次都没有期待过开学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 今年…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 堀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们分在几班？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,1班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,堀也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 哪儿都没看到透的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明明在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在1班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村也在同一个班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是一副死宅相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,由纪 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,堀 再把笔记借我抄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你好歹也自己做一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,座位已经确定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请 请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,堀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 我们座位很近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像是以前的3班重聚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都回位坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是1班的班主任 寺岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,教的科目是化学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家多多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后说一下今天的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.24,Note,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H55&\b1\frz339.8\pos(270.441,223.765)}落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,9点开始开学典礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我们的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是被狗吓到 然后跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你特地送他回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,创太君很懂事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,名字和住址都能很清楚的说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是被很好的教导过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也没有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,家务都是自己做 很了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是令人意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你是堀同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我是堀没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 你是跟我同校的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我是跟你同班的宫村呀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.00,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(55.861,207.772)}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.00,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(112.567,221.133)}请不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.00,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(171.532,208.107)}这边的角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.00,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(230.402,243.107)}没事的 我真得会待在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.00,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(653.459,169.155)}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:43.00,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(595.011,189.155)}请不要跟我搭话
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「我是跟你同班的宫村呀」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,发 发型变了 感觉完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学你也是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(59.416,211.575)}对不起我没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(108.288,145.799)}诶？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(426.669,230.907)}又不肯脱的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(480.148,228.712)}你怎么老是一副热得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(536.588,240.392)}太好啦终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(591.712,213.641)}下节课是体育吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(660.829,202.903)}宫村你让开点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.17,Screen-1,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H18&\frz270\pos(702.334,184.903)}真是的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,「堀同学你也是呢」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是居家型的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我的素颜连由纪都没给看过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拼图有一块我不会拼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这片你放反了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以一起吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么啦 两人份三人份也没差多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你的那份都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你平时也用这个发型不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜也不用戴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是耳洞太显眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学也是 不化妆更可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个表情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 还要再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,「再来」什么的是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,创 创太说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,「还想再和大哥哥一起玩」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以下次休息日…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是创太…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,从那开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我就常在休息日去堀同学家里作客了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是每个休息日都去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样的日子 现在也持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.66,upper,,0,0,0,,然后呀 透就呆掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:30.66,upper,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个大男生还哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还不是因为你踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫『下踢腿』啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,又要叫你姐姐来救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的叫做「姐控」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,姐 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,创太 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去星巴克喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,星巴克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就和创太一起回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我的那份果汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 这不是拿铁咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 你不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看创太怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌「下踢腿」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办 堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有体检…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天不是通知了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 到这种地方来要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这个要怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,居然有刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的都不知道该说你是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还是蠢好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 堀同学你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,会被停学…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 会被退学的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力竹笋真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能大喊『性骚扰』躲过一劫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,最近你和堀走得很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在 在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你和堀完全不是一个世界的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我和堀同学一点也不般配
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不…般配…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,给我说明白呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你喜欢堀同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是又怎么样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.79,Screen-2,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H34&\frz270\fad(208,0)\pos(606.99,176.263)}天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:56.97,Screen-2,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H34&\frz270\pos(688.951,216.962)}天然呆模式全开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.73,Screen-2,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H34&\frz270\pos(644.156,243.944)}真的只是天然呆而已
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是啊 那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以每次我和堀同学讲话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你都在后面盯着…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,声音太大了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 这是秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:09:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个在这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下节是体育课吧 快去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也是迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们动作慢点也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你这换得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就想问了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么夏天也穿着冬天的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是有什么伤痕之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不…也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然在这里说有点那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我的身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要跟别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 是真的纹上去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这个穿衬衫确实是会透出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来既然知道要藏 一开始就不要纹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也有「意识到这些的时候已经纹上去了」的情况嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得你这家伙很有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是堀喜欢的脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,居然连耳洞都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,堀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才和透在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不要移开视线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我的眼睛说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是我做了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,创太就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以跟堀告白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛要征求我的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是由堀同学决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我看上去和堀同学关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是除了朋友关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们两个交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那我算什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一定很碍眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,「{\alphaFF\t(0,800,\alpha00)}堀{\alphaFF\t(1000,1800,\alpha00)}创{\alphaFF\t(1800,2500,\alpha00)}太」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我写好了哟 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,写得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吃布丁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就习惯孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过是回到了从前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我正准备吃布丁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（不行了）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（你完了）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,透都跟我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,会说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,「把钥匙还给我」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,「不要再来我家了」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和 和我不般配什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真心这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我做你的朋友什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这种话是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 比起这些 石川君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村 你说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就像石川同学说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个人又阴暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,又不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得是不是给堀同学添麻烦了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我虽然不是真的那么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不想堀同学的人气因为和我做朋友而下降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 没关系的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要在意我的人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不许再说这种话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我还可以再来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村你要是不来了 创太会哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人买东西也会很累
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,食材什么的 也会多出来的好吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,透？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我拒绝他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 他是个不错的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要是看到我的素颜一定会吓一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君才不会那样呢 他是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村你喜欢透吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去和他交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君那么帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我配不上他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在伤心中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好好说「早上好」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉透今天一直在躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,堀你不觉得和他讲话会很尴尬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.90,Screen-2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\pos(25.479,209.482)}完全不觉得
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的透…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不觉得和他讲话会尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上石川君很平常的对我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,「宫村早上好 作业做完了吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很平常的朋友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村 在偷懒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是跑不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,流了好多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么今天就以4人为一组
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,完成报告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可以自由组合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吉川 借我一支笔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你有很多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会借给说这种话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有谁带了资料集吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,纸够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有活页纸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村 你来总结图表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 那是我的橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我就借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别用新角去擦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来 两人一组手拉手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一起手拉手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来 和我手拉手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都拉好了手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是什么坏人 但是有点阴暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,又是宫村落单了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就没哪个组能收一下他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的生活一直都是我的日常…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 宫村你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,第五节保健课改成政经了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道带了课本没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不希望这样临时调课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 堀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她也太镇定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一般会觉得尴尬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然她要是真尴尬了 我也会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可能她真的是完全不在乎我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君算是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呀 这事宫村你怎么看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 什么怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这种话你直接问出来让人觉得很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你和堀那么要好也让我很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说话不清不楚的时候让人很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候行为举止奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,滥好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,容易吃亏 让人放不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,掀起头发摘下眼镜看起来比女生还漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,都让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这些话还是让我说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点是让我最火大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你一个人用姓加「君」来称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是担心你是怎么看我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,透…透…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思的话就不要勉强自己叫啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心 恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我就是叫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,叫一下而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是因为我第一次叫同学的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很奇怪 但我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是有些笨拙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,伊澄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了在午休的时候要完成报告的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋二人组
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,加上吉川 是笨蛋三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等会要好好完成报告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听说下节课是在视听教室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要带课本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,高三
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,春天才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在和你相遇之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在和你相遇之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我家见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村同学
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
